==Arabic alphabet==

===Letter===
'''{{ARchar|و / ‍و}}''' (wāw)

# The twenty-seventh letter of the [[Arabic]] alphabet. It is preceded by {{ARchar|[[ه]]}} and followed by {{ARchar|[[ى]]}}.
# The sixth letter in traditional [[abjad]] order, which is used in place of numerals for list numbering ([[abjad numerals]]). It is preceded by {{ARchar|[[ه]]}} and followed by {{ARchar|[[ز]]}}.

[[Category:Abjad numerals|06]]

